        <!-- ============================================================
             HOW TO SHIP AN UPDATE
             ============================================================
             1. Build a Release archive in Xcode → export as "Developer ID"
             2. Zip the .app: ditto -c -k -sequesterRsrc -keepParent Photiva.app Photiva-X.Y.zip
             3. Generate the EdDSA signature:
                    ~/Library/Developer/Xcode/DerivedData/Photiva-*/SourcePackages/artifacts/sparkle/Sparkle/bin/sign_update Photiva-X.Y.zip
             4. Upload the zip to the photivareleases repo
             5. Duplicate the latest <item> below, fill in version/url/length/signature
             6. Commit this file and push — Vercel will deploy the updated appcast
             ============================================================ -->

